# Demo Test Steps

1. Open Dolibarr locally at `http://localhost/dolibarr/htdocs`.
2. Confirm Products, Stocks, Barcode, and TakePOS modules are enabled and configured.
3. Open product `Peach Cider`.
4. Confirm starting stock is 6 units in GS-MAIN warehouse.
5. Open TakePOS.
6. Add two Peach Ciders to the cart.
7. Complete the sale.
8. Return to the product stock screen.
9. Confirm stock decreased from 6 to 4.
